---
import { Collapse, Spoiler, Timeline } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
import Substats from '@/components/about/Substats.astro'
import ToolSection from '@/components/about/ToolSection.astro'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'education', text: 'Education' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'tools', text: 'Tools' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'social-networks', text: 'Social Networks' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'gossips', text: 'Gossips' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'about-blog', text: 'About Blog' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='About' {headings} comment>
  <p>
    Developer / <s>College Student</s>
  </p>
  <p>
    你好，我是 Layden，是一名刚刚进入 C/<s>C++</s> 开发领域的菜鸟。<br />
    平时喜欢打 CS，最近迷上了瓦罗兰特，有大佬请务必带带我。
  </p>
  <p>
    Motto: Bedlocked. <Spoiler>躺平不是摆烂，是在给电池充电。</Spoiler>
  </p>

  {/* education */}
  <h2 id='education'>Education</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>合肥工业大学 (Hefei University of Technology), 2021–2025</li>
  </ul>

  {/* tools */}
  <h2 id='tools'>Tools</h2>
  <p>Current support tools as follow:</p>
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Productivity'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Chrome',
        description: 'Browser',
        href: 'https://www.google.com/chrome/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/chrome.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Microsoft Edge',
        description: 'Browser',
        href: 'https://www.microsoft.com/edge',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/edge.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Obsidian',
        description: 'Notes',
        href: 'https://obsidian.md/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/obsidian.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Development'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'VS Code',
        description: 'IDE',
        href: 'https://code.visualstudio.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/vscode.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Cursor',
        description: 'Editor',
        href: 'https://www.cursor.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/cursor.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Claude Code',
        description: 'Terminal coding agent',
        href: 'https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/overview',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/claude.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Gemini',
        description: 'AI assistant',
        href: 'https://gemini.google.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/gemini.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Codex',
        description: 'Terminal coding agent',
        href: 'https://developers.openai.com/codex/cli',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/codex.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Environment'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Arch Linux',
        description: 'Linux Distribution',
        href: 'https://archlinux.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/archlinux.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Ubuntu 24.04 LTS',
        description: 'Linux Distribution',
        href: 'https://ubuntu.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/ubuntu.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'MacOS Tahoe',
        description: 'MacBook Air',
        href: 'https://www.apple.com/macos/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/apple.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Windows 11',
        description: 'Framework Laptop 16',
        href: 'https://news.microsoft.com/windows11-general-availability/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/windows11.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* social-networks */}
  <h2 id='social-networks'>Social Networks</h2>
  <p>Mostly on GitHub:</p>
  <Substats
    stats={[
      {
        platform: 'GitHub',
        icon: 'github',
        link: 'https://github.com/just-liedown',
        text: 'followers',
        api: 'github/just-liedown'
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* gossips */}
  <h2 id='gossips'>Gossips</h2>
  <Collapse title='Lorem ipsum'>
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, vidit suscipit at mei. Quem denique mea id. Usu ei regione indoctum
    dissentiunt, cu meliore fuisset mei, vel quod voluptua ne. Ex dicat impedit mel, at eum oratio
    possit voluptatum.
  </Collapse>

  {/* about-blog */}
  <h2 id='about-blog'>About Blog</h2>
  <p>Website history:</p>
  <Timeline
    events={[
      {
        date: '2024-04-29',
        content:
          'Website refactored using <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro</a> and <a href="https://github.com/srleom/astro-theme-resume" target="_blank">Astro Theme Resume</a>'
      },
      {
        date: '2024-07-26',
        content:
          'Website abstracted as a theme and published on <a href="https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure"target="_blank">Github</a>'
      },
      {
        date: '2024-07-27',
        content: 'Began writing website docs'
      }
    ]}
  />
  <p>
    The smooth operation and personalized customization of website also rely on the resources and
    technical support provided by the following excellent projects/service providers:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Domain: <a href='#' target='_blank'>Vercel</a></li>
    <li>
      Framework & Theme: <a href='https://astro.build/' target='_blank'>Astro</a> + <a
        href='https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure'
        target='_blank'>Astro Theme Pure</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Site hosting: <a href='https://vercel.com/' target='_blank'>Vercel</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      CI/CD: <a href='https://vercel.com/workflow' target='_blank'>Vercel Workflow</a>
    </li>
    <li>Comment system: <a href='https://waline.js.org' target='_blank'>Waline</a></li>
    <li>
      Visits: <a href='https://supabase.com/' target='_blank'>Supabase</a> +
      <a href='https://waline.js.org/' target='_blank'>Waline</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      Other statistics: <a href='https://github.com/spencerwooo/substats' target='_blank'
        >Substats</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>
</PageLayout>
